PrecisAuthority to enter into a real estate transaction with ERIC RUSSELL LAWRENCE, of the Town of Maple Creek, Saskatchewan, wherein the Crown will acquire title to some 32.85 hectares of land which are required in connection with the GAP CREEK DIVERSION WEIR and, IN EXCHANGE, Mr. Lawrence will acquire title to some 37.79 hectares of land together with an attendant easement.
